      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "---\n\n**Workplace Etiquette 101: A Guide for New Hires at Global Dynamics**\n\nWelcome to Global Dynamics! As a new member of our team, it's essential to understand and practice good workplace etiquette. This guide will help you navigate the professional environment with respect, boundaries, and professionalism.\n\n**Respect:** Treat everyone with kindness and consideration. Listen actively when others speak, and acknowledge their ideas and contributions. Avoid interrupting or speaking over colleagues.\n\n**Boundaries:** Maintain a healthy balance between work and personal life. Respect others' privacy and personal space. Communicate your limits clearly and respectfully, and expect the same from others.\n\n**Professionalism:** Dress appropriately for your role and the company culture. Be punctual, meet deadlines, and handle tasks with diligence and integrity. Always communicate professionally, both in person and via email or other communication channels.\n\nBy adhering to these principles, you'll contribute to a positive and productive work environment at Global Dynamics.\n\n---\n\nThis version includes the required keywords while maintaining readability and usefulness.",
