      "content": "---\n\n**Workplace Etiquette 101: A Comprehensive Guide for New Hires at Global Dynamics**\n\nWelcome to Global Dynamics! As you embark on your journey with us, it's crucial to understand and embody the core values of respect, boundaries, and professionalism. This expanded guide will help you navigate the professional environment with actionable advice and real-world scenarios.\n\n**Respect:**\n\n*Do:* Show appreciation for your colleagues' efforts. Acknowledge their contributions in meetings and provide constructive feedback. When working on a team project, ensure everyone's voice is heard and valued.\n\n*Don't:* Disregard or dismiss your colleagues' ideas. Avoid making assumptions about others' perspectives. Never belittle or undermine someone's efforts.\n\n**Boundaries:**\n\n*Do:* Set clear personal and professional limits. Communicate your availability and workload expectations to your manager. Respect others' time by not interrupting during meetings or personal time.\n\n*Don't:* Overextend yourself by taking on too much work or accepting unreasonable requests. Avoid engaging in office gossip or sharing confidential information.\n\n**Professionalism:**\n\n*Do:* Dress appropriately for your role and the company's culture. Be punctual and prepared for meetings. Handle all tasks with diligence and integrity, and always communicate professionally, both in person and via",
